<h3 class="govuk-heading-m">How to find your login credentials</h3>

<ol class="govuk-list govuk-list--number govuk-list--spaced">
  <li>
    <strong>Open the CloudFormation console</strong>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      Go to <a href="https://us-east-1.console.aws.amazon.com/cloudformation/home?region=us-east-1#/stacks" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="govuk-link">CloudFormation console in us-east-1<span class="govuk-visually-hidden"> (opens in new tab)</span></a>
    </p>
  </li>

  <li>
    <strong>Find your stack</strong>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      Look for a stack containing <code>bops-planning</code> in the name.
      The status should be <span class="govuk-tag govuk-tag--green">CREATE_COMPLETE</span>
    </p>
  </li>

  <li>
    <strong>Go to the Outputs tab</strong>
    <p class="govuk-body">Click the stack name, then select the <strong>Outputs</strong> tab. You'll see:</p>
    <table class="govuk-table">
      <thead class="govuk-table__head">
        <tr class="govuk-table__row">
          <th class="govuk-table__header">Output</th>
          <th class="govuk-table__header">What it is</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody class="govuk-table__body">
        <tr class="govuk-table__row">
          <td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>BOPSLoginUrl</code></td>
          <td class="govuk-table__cell">The login page URL (via CloudFront HTTPS)</td>
        </tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row">
          <td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>BOPSUsername</code></td>
          <td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>ndx-demo_assessor@example.com</code> (or administrator/reviewer)</td>
        </tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row">
          <td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>BOPSPassword</code></td>
          <td class="govuk-table__cell">The admin password (shown in plain text)</td>
        </tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row">
          <td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>ApplicantsPortalUrl</code></td>
          <td class="govuk-table__cell">The public-facing applicants portal (for Step 4)</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </li>

  <li>
    <strong>Log in</strong>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      Open the <code>BOPSLoginUrl</code> in a new tab. Enter the email <code>ndx-demo_assessor@example.com</code> and the password shown in the <code>BOPSPassword</code> output.
    </p>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      You should see "Signed in successfully" and be taken to the <strong>My Applications</strong> dashboard showing planning cases assigned to you.
    </p>
  </li>
</ol>

<div class="govuk-inset-text">
  <strong>Three user roles are available:</strong>
  <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
    <li><code>ndx-demo_assessor@example.com</code> — case officer (sees assigned applications)</li>
    <li><code>ndx-demo_reviewer@example.com</code> — reviewer (reviews recommendations)</li>
    <li><code>ndx-demo_administrator@example.com</code> — admin (manages users, settings)</li>
  </ul>
  <p class="govuk-body">All three use the same password shown in the <code>BOPSPassword</code> output.</p>
</div>
